### ðŸ”¹ STEP 6: Test the API with Postman (Optional, but recommended)

Use [Postman](https://www.postman.com/) or Thunder Client (VS Code extension) to:

1. Test `POST /api/auth/register`:

   ```json
   {
     "username": "john",
     "email": "john@example.com",
     "password": "123456"
   }
   ```

2. Then test `POST /api/auth/login`:

   ```json
   {
     "email": "john@example.com",
     "password": "123456"
   }
   ```

âœ… You should get a **JWT token** and user data.

